WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.044
Myocarditis — inflammatory disease of the myocardium

00:00:03.044 --> 00:00:06.088
— remains one of the most diagnostically

00:00:06.088 --> 00:00:09.132
challenging and clinically underestimated conditions in cardiology.

00:00:09.132 --> 00:00:12.176
With an estimated global incidence between 1

00:00:12.176 --> 00:00:15.220
and 10 cases per 100,000 population annually,

00:00:15.220 --> 00:00:18.264
it accounts for a significant proportion of

00:00:18.264 --> 00:00:21.308
sudden cardiac deaths in patients under 35.

00:00:21.308 --> 00:00:24.352
This presentation reviews the major adverse effects,

00:00:24.352 --> 00:00:27.395
diagnostic criteria, and current management strategies relevant

00:00:27.395 --> 00:00:28.700
to clinical practice.
